&#160;<a href=\"/Penny\" title=\"Penny\">Penny</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sebastian\" title=\"Sebastian\"><img alt=\"Sebastian Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/6a/Sebastian_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sebastian\" title=\"Sebastian\">Sebastian</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\"><img alt=\"Vincent Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/0/0b/Vincent_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\">Vincent</a></span>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Bundles\">Bundles</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Beer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Bundles\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Beer is not used in any <a href=\"/Bundles\" title=\"Bundles\">bundles</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Beer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Tailoring\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Beer is used in the spool of the <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane#Sewing_Machine\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">Sewing Machine</a> with <a href=\"/Cloth\" title=\"Cloth\">Cloth</a> in the feed to create a <link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplateinline\"><img alt=\"Shirt138.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/e/e4/Shirt138.png/24px-Shirt138.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/e/e4/Shirt138.png 1.5x\" /> <a href=\"/Tailoring\" title=\"Tailoring\">Black Leather Jacket</a></span>. It is a yellow dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed. It can be placed in the yellow dye pot at <a href=\"/Emily\" title=\"Emily\">Emily</a>'s and <a href=\"/Haley\" title=\"Haley\">Haley</a>'s house, <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">2 Willow Lane</a>, for use in <a href=\"/Dyeing\" title=\"Dyeing\">dyeing</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quests\">Quests</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Beer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Quests\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Beer is not used in any <a href=\"/Quests\" title=\"Quests\">quests</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Beer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.0\" title=\"Version History\">1.0</a>: Introduced.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.1\" title=\"Version History\">1.1</a>: Added ability to age in <a href=\"/Cask\" title=\"Cask\">casks</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.4\" title=\"Version History\">1.4</a>: Can now be used in <a href=\"/Tailoring\" title=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.6\" title=\"Version History\">1.6</a>: Now purchasable from <a href=\"/Desert_Festival\" title=\"Desert Festival\">Desert Festival</a>.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Artisan_Goods\" title=\"Artisan Goods\">Artisan Goods</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Bee_House\" title=\"Bee House\">Bee House</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Honey\" title=\"Honey\">Honey</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Cask\" title=\"Cask\">Cask</a>\n</th>\n<td><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Beer</a> • <