moker</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Smoked_Fish\" title=\"Smoked Fish\">Smoked Fish</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Dehydrator\" title=\"Dehydrator\">Dehydrator</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Dried_Mushrooms\" title=\"Dried Mushrooms\">Dried Mushrooms</a> • <a href=\"/Dried_Fruit\" title=\"Dried Fruit\">Dried Fruit</a> • <a href=\"/Raisins\" title=\"Raisins\">Raisins</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Misc\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Maple_Syrup\" title=\"Maple Syrup\">Maple Syrup</a> • <a href=\"/Oak_Resin\" title=\"Oak Resin\">Oak Resin</a> • <a href=\"/Pine_Tar\" title=\"Pine Tar\">Pine Tar</a>  • <a href=\"/Mystic_Syrup\" title=\"Mystic Syrup\">Mystic Syrup</a>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260413162114\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.192 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.213 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3936/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 80845/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 3474/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 17/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 12104/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.015/7.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 1.19 MB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  114.028      1 -total\n 81.22%   92.612      1 Template:Infobox\n 27.57%   31.433      1 Template:EdibilityGrid\n 25.38%   28.938      8 Template:Qualityprice\n 12.19%   13.898     20 Template:Overlayimg\n 10.54%   12.021      5 Template:Name\n 10.43%   11.889      1 Template:Description\n  5.09%    5.801      1 Template:GiftsByItem\n  3.75%    4.276      2 Template:Duration\n  2.89%    3.301      4 Template:History\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:2083-0!canonical and timestamp 20260413162114 and revision id 177001\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "{{Infobox\n|eng             = Beer\n|source          = <nowiki />\n*[[Artisan Goods]]\n*[[The Stardrop Saloon|The Saloon]]\n*[[Ginger Island#Island South|Ginger Island Resort]]\n|buff            = {{Name|Tipsy|link=Buffs#Tipsy{{!}}Tipsy}}{{Name|Speed|−1}}\n|buffduration    = 30s\n|edibility       = 20\n|sellprice       = 200\n|ingredients     = {{Name|Wheat|1}}\n|craftingstation = {{Name|Keg}}\n|crafttime       = 1750m (&#8776;29h)\n}}\n'''Beer''' is an [[Artisan Goods|Artisan Good]] made from the [[Keg]] using [[Wheat]], taking 1-2 days. It is also available at [[The Stardrop Saloon|The Saloon]] for {{Price|400}} and the [[Ginger Island#Island South|Ginger Island Resort]] for {{Price|500}}.  It can also be received as a gift at the [[Feast of the Winter Star]]. [[Pam]] sells Beer in her [[Desert Festival#Villager Shops|shop]] at the [[Desert Festival]] for {{Price|20|Calico}} [[Calico Egg]]s.\n\nWhen consumed, Beer causes a [[Buffs|Tipsy Buff]] that decreases [[Speed]] by 1.\n\n==Aged Values==\nBeer can be placed inside a [[Cask]] to age from normal quality to silver, gold, and eventually iridium quality. Iridium quality doubles the base sell price of Beer.  \n\nNormal, silver, and gold quality Beer can be prematurely removed from a cask at any time by striking the cask with an [[Axes|Axe]], [[Hoes|Hoe]], or [[Pickaxes|Pickaxe]].\n\n{|class=\"wikitable roundedborder\"\n!Normal Quality\n!Silver Quality<br />(x 1.25)\n!Gold Quality<br />(x 1.5)\n!Iridium Quality<br />(x 2)\n|-\n|{{Qualityprice|Beer|200|quality=normal|dsv=false}}\n|{{Qualityprice|Beer|200|quality=silver|dsv=false}} ''Aged: 7 Days''\n|{{Qualityprice|Beer|200|quality=gold|dsv=false}} ''Aged: 7 Days<br />Total: 14 Days''\n|{{Qualityprice|Beer|200|quality=iridium|dsv=false}} ''Aged: 14 Days<br />Total: 28 Days''\n|-\n|}\n\n==Gifting==\n{{GiftsByItem\n|like=Robin,Demetrius,Maru,Linus,Pierre,Caroline,Abigail,Alex,George,Evelyn,Lewis,Clint,Emily,Haley,Jodi,Kent,Sam,Leah,Marnie,Elliott,Gus,Dwarf,Wizard,Harvey,Sandy,Willy,Krobus\n|hate=Sebastian,Penny,Jas,Vincent,Leo\n|love=Pam,Shane\n}}\n\n==Bundles==\nBeer is not used in any [[bundles]].\n\n==Tailoring==\nBeer is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] with [[Cloth]] in the feed to create a {{Name|Shirt138|link=Tailoring{{!}}Black Leather Jacket|class=inline}}. It is a yellow dye when used in the spool of the Sewing Machine with a dyeable clothing item in the feed. It can be placed in the yellow dye pot at [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]], for use in [[dyeing]].\n\n==Quests==\nBeer is not used in any [[quests]].\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.0|Introduced.}}\n{{History|1.1|Added ability to age in [[cask]]s.}}\n{{History|1.4|Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].}}\n{{History|1.6|Now purchasable from [[Desert Festival]].}}\n\n{{NavboxArtisanGoods}}\n\n[[Category:Artisan Goods]]\n\n[[de:Bier]]\n[[es:Cerveza]]\n[[fr:Bière]]\n[[it:Birra]]\n[[ja:ビール]]\n[[ko:맥주]]\n[[hu:Sör]]\n[[pt:Cerveja]]\n[[ru:Пиво]]\n[[tr:Bira]]\n[[zh:啤酒]]"
